rgence OR config.maxIterations, whichever comes first), and phase_synthesis.\nWrite all outputs to .opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/015-per-skill-improvement-research/003-motion/research/lineages/gpt55fast. Do not touch any path outside .opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/015-per-skill-improvement-research/003-motion/research/lineages/gpt55fast.\n\nWhen complete, output a single line: FANOUT_LINEAGE_COMPLETE:gpt55fast","specFolder":".opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/154-sk-design-parent/015-per-skill-improvement-research/003-motion","tenantId":"","userId":"","agentId":"","limit":5,"session_id":"fanout-gpt55fast-1782532104406-n794vy","turnNumber":1,"include_cognitive":true},"error":"{\n  \"summary\": \"Error: sessionId \\\"fanout-gpt55fast-1782532104406-n794vy\\\" does not match a server-managed session. Omit sessionId to start a new server-generated session and reuse the effectiveSessionId returned by the server.\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"error\": \"sessionId \\\"fanout-gpt55fast-1782532104406-n794vy\\\" does not match a server-managed session. Omit sessionId to start a new server-generated session and reuse the effectiveSessionId returned by the server.\",\n    \"code\": \"E_SESSION_SCOPE\",\n    \"details\": {\n      \"requestedSessionId\": \"fanout-gpt55fast-1782532104406-n794vy\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"hints\": [\n    \"Omit session_id to start a new server-generated session, or reuse the effectiveSessionId returned by memory_context.\"\n  ],\n  \"meta\": {\n    \"tool\": \"memory_match_triggers\",\n    \"tokenCount\": 226,\n    \"cacheHit\": false,\n    \"isError\": true,\n    \"severity\": \"error\",\n    \"tokenBudget\": 3500\n  }\n}","time":{"start":1782532161068,"end":1782532180270}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_0d7dbb664bba8400016a3f482a16cc8191b4cbda2f4932266b"}},"id":"prt_f0731e465001gKWNLWDz0RCKgW","sessionID":"ses_0f8ce9c93ffeovEiyqk3ArIgPy","messageID":"msg_f07316a0f001SiT0QIB97xtM