{"type":"text","timestamp":1782532593667,"sessionID":"ses_0f8ce9c93ffeovEiyqk3ArIgPy","part":{"id":"prt_f0738d4950018VCSYdO7A9lKR3","messageID":"msg_f073833280019jPO7t64RMrgmG","sessionID":"ses_0f8ce9c93ffeovEiyqk3ArIgPy","type":"text","text":"Phase main loop will converge in six evidence iterations rather than exhaust ten: the corpus and live packet agree on most completed work, and the remaining findings are residual, bounded improvements. I’m creating only lineage-local state and output files now.","time":{"start":1782532592789,"end":1782532593665},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_097d939d875b9bc2016a3f49f0c8408191a1e0defd0ffce5c4","phase":"commentary"}}}}
